Interface DSIStorable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DSFlexEnum, DSJavaEnum, DSPasswordAes, DSPasswordSha256, DSStatus

    public interface DSIStorable
    Enables custom serialization for non-node values in the configuration database. Not used for DSA interop.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      DSIValue restore(DSElement element)

      DSElement store()
      Serialize the value for the configuration database.
